  m_text: 'PP - Plutonic Points, collect these by romancing the alien (required for
    abilities in "Escape From Area 51")


    Money - Collect around Area 51 (Required
    to buy gifts from Davids Extraspectacular Second Hand Thrift Store, accessible
    via clicking on the business card in the lower right)


    Day/Night - current
    time and date (you have 7 days to successfully romance and help the alien break
    out of Area 51)'
